'''Attack pattern Ignimus''' was an infantry attack tactic used by small [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] ground forces.<ref name="SWG:Fotp" />

==History==
After the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], this tactic was used by an [[Inquisitorium hunter]] and an [[Inquisitorium dark trooper]] that attacked the [[Dark Jedi/Legends|Dark Jedi]] [[Xos]] on the planet [[Mustafar/Legends|Mustafar]].<ref name="SWG:Fotp" />

